of Young Master?

00:06:40.277 --> 00:06:42.316
We have spent much time together.

00:06:42.317 --> 00:06:44.238
It's only natural

00:06:44.317 --> 00:06:45.758
to share each other's scent.

00:06:46.798 --> 00:06:48.357
I knew you two get along best

00:06:48.358 --> 00:06:49.837
with each other.

00:06:51.118 --> 00:06:52.677
I almost forgot what I came for.

00:06:52.678 --> 00:06:53.597
Where's my mother?

00:06:53.598 --> 00:06:54.797
