00:07:29.238 --> 00:07:30.358
Li Yue,

00:07:30.798 --> 00:07:31.836
you used dark sorcery

00:07:31.837 --> 00:07:34.037
to assume my appearance and identity.

00:07:34.238 --> 00:07:36.238
You obtained everything you desired.

00:07:36.957 --> 00:07:38.877
What else do you want now?

00:07:38.878 --> 00:07:40.557
My son is Wujing City Young Lord,

00:07:40.558 --> 00:07:42.358
but he's blind.

00:07:42.478 --> 00:07:45.997
My appearance is slowly returning
to its former ugliness.

00:07:45.998 --> 00:07:48.276
People will eventually find out I'm not

00:07:48.277 --> 00:07:50.678
of the Wujing Saintess' bloodline.

00:07:50.757 --> 00:07:52.477
Bloodline matters

00:07:52.478 --> 00:07:54.438
can only be resolved
through reincarnation.

00:07:54.558 --> 00:07:56.316
After all, what you stole

00:07:56.317 --> 00:07:58.558
was never yours to take.

00:07:59.197 --> 00:08:00.438
Yes.

00:08:00.678 --> 00:08:03.758
But I heard
before you returned to Wujing City,

00:08:04.438 --> 00:08:07.198
