00:08:11.038 --> 00:08:13.558
After all, she is the bloodline
of the Wujing Saintess.

00:08:13.637 --> 00:08:15.878
She is to marry a Dragon

00:08:16.397 --> 00:08:18.118
and become the Dragon Queen.

00:08:19.517 --> 00:08:20.997
Li Yue, you...

00:08:20.998 --> 00:08:23.357
So do you want your daughter dead

00:08:23.358 --> 00:08:25.998
