to see the light of day again.

00:08:35.358 --> 00:08:37.558
I want eternal youth.

00:08:37.798 --> 00:08:39.676
I want everyone to believe

00:08:39.677 --> 00:08:40.756
that I

00:08:40.757 --> 00:08:43.558
am the true bloodline
of the Wujing Saintess.

00:08:44.358 --> 00:08:45.877
What about my daughter?

00:08:45.878 --> 00:08:48.117
I will bring her back to Wujing City,

00:08:48.118 --> 00:08:50.077
grant her the status of a princess,

00:08:50.238 --> 00:08:53.638
and let her
become the future Dragon Queen.

00:08:53.718 --> 00:08:54.678
Don't harm my daughter!

00:08:56.118 --> 00:08:57.197
Don't harm my daughter.

00:08:57.198 --> 00:08:58.198
Mother.

00:08:59.557 --> 00:09:00.237
Don't be afraid.

00:09:00.238 --> 00:09:02.318
- Don't harm my daughter.
- Don't be afraid, Mother.

00:09:02.557 --> 00:09:04.469
I have rescued you from the dungeon.

00:09:04.470 --> 00:09:05.709
You will no longer suffer.

00:09:05.710 --> 00:09:06.790
It's alright now.

00:09:06.870 --> 00:09:07.990
You're alright.

00:09:08.157 --> 00:09:09.158
Feng Manor...

00:09:09.797 --> 00:09:10.556
Feng Manor...

00:09:10.557 --> 00:09:12.756
Feng Manor will protect my child, right?

00:09:12.757 --> 00:09:13.436
Yes.

00:09:13.437 --> 00:09:14.077
Yes.

00:09:14.078 --> 00:09:15.638
I brought this on my daughter.

00:09:16.557 --> 00:09:17.237
No.

00:09:17.238 --> 00:09:17.997
My daughter...

00:09:17.998 --> 00:09:19.717
My daughter is surely in Wujing.

00:09:19.718 --> 00:09:21.237
She must be in Wujing.

00:09:21.797 --> 00:09:22.757
No.

00:09:22.998 --> 00:09:23.756
Wait, no.

00:09:23.757 --> 00:09:25.357
