Where is she?

00:09:30.838 --> 00:09:31.717
I am right here.

00:09:31.757 --> 00:09:32.717
Mother,

00:09:33.517 --> 00:09:34.997
I am by your side.

00:09:34.998 --> 00:09:37.237
Is she at Feng Manor or Wujing City?

00:09:37.757 --> 00:09:39.077
I am before you,

00:09:39.078 --> 00:09:39.837
Mother.

00:09:39.838 --> 00:09:40.837
No.

00:09:41.318 --> 00:09:42.558
It's alright, Mother.

00:09:44.238 --> 00:09:45.997
I will take you back to Feng Manor.

00:09:46.037 --> 00:09:47.558
Everything will get better.

00:09:47.797 --> 00:09:48.957
It's alright.

00:09:49.118 --> 00:09:49.676
My daughter.

00:09:49.677 --> 00:09:50.798
It's alright.

00:09:56.718 --> 00:09:57.477
Your Grace,

00:09:57.637 --> 00:09:58.357
