00:09:58.358 --> 00:10:00.678
to search the Young Lord's
Dongming Hall.

00:10:00.718 --> 00:10:02.638
There is no sign of Yue.

00:10:03.397 --> 00:10:05.556
Feng Zhilou and Li Yan must have

00:10:05.557 --> 00:10:07.357
rescued her together.

00:10:07.677 --> 00:10:09.717
We have searched everywhere.

00:10:09.718 --> 00:10:11.597
Where else could they be hiding her?

00:10:12.637 --> 00:10:14.438
That wretched Feng Zhilou.

00:10:14.797 --> 00:10:16.877
Not only is Prince Shang protecting her,

00:10:16.878 --> 00:10:18.556
but she also stole my blood vessel.

00:10:18.557 --> 00:10:20.638
How am I to survive
until the wedding day?

00:10:20.878 --> 00:10:21.796
Where is Baiyue?

00:10:21.797 --> 00:10:23.036
What is he up to these days?

00:10:23.037 --> 00:10:25.237
The Dragon Prince
of the sanctuary has arrived.

00:10:25.358 --> 00:10:28.318
Princess Liluo, please come out
to greet him at once.

00:10:38.318 --> 00:10:39.997
Why are you here?

00:10:41.277 --> 00:10:43.077
I came to check on you

00:10:43.078 --> 00:10:45.077
and see what you plan to do next.

00:10:45.198 --> 00:10:46.638
You're asking me?

00:10:46.998 --> 00:10:49.357
You Dragons betrayed your word.

00:10:49.517 --> 00:10:52.278
I should be the one
asking what you plan to do.

00:10:53.318 --> 00:10:55.997
Are you planning
to eliminate Feng Zhilou

00:10:56.277 --> 00:10:58.597
or continue to seduce my brother

00:10:58.598 --> 00:11:00.717
until he agrees to marry you

00:11:01.238 --> 00:11:02.438
even though

00:11:02.677 --> 00:11:05.997
you have already proven
you're the Wujing Saintess?

00:11:07.277 --> 00:11:08.518
Prince Zhi,

00:11:09.277 --> 00:11:11.597
don't think I don't know
what you're thinking.

00:11:11.598 --> 00:11:13.756
A Dragon Prince
cannot become the Dragon King

00:11:13.757 --> 00:11:15.477
without marrying the Wujing Saintess.

00:11:15.917 --> 00:11:16.837
You

00:11:17.437 --> 00:11:19.518
are just a supporting act.

00:11:23.198 --> 00:11:25.477
Precisely because of this,

00:11:25.598 --> 00:11:28.518
we ought to sympathize with each other.

00:11:30.917 --> 00:11:33.036
In our families,

00:11:33.037 --> 00:11:34.997
we've always fallen short
of their full regard.

00:11:36.318 --> 00:11:37.638
And you,

00:11:37.958 --> 00:11:39.757
as the Wujing Saintess,

00:11:40.118 --> 00:11:42.638
have been rejected by Prince Shang.

00:11:42.838 --> 00:11:44.077
As for me,

00:11:44.358 --> 00:11:46.357
I am the Dragon Prince,

00:11:46.358 --> 00:11:47.796
but in my father's eyes,

00:11:47.797 --> 00:11:49.918
he only ever wishes
to see his other son.

00:11:53.277 --> 00:11:54.957
You mean to say

00:11:54.958 --> 00:11:56.916
we are fellow sufferers?

00:11:56.917 --> 00:11:57.436
No.

00:11:57.437 --> 00:11:58.837
I prefer

00:11:58.878 --> 00:12:00.798
a strong alliance.

00:12:13.517 --> 00:12:15.158
My sight is much better than before.

00:12:15.757 --> 00:12:17.318
Besides seeing colors,

00:12:17.557 --> 00:12:19.278
I can make out some shapes now.

00:12:28.238 --> 00:12:29.357
Xiaoyu,

00:12:30.157 --> 00:12:31.318
what's wrong?

00:13:00.557 --> 00:13:03.396
You always carry the fragrance
of various herbs

00:13:03.397 --> 00:13:04.877
from the apothecary.

00:13:05.318 --> 00:13:07.117
It's a soothing scent.

00:13:11.677 --> 00:13:12.638
Xiaoyu,

00:13:13.517 --> 00:13:15.077
how is the night tonight?

00:13:33.037 --> 00:13:35.518
As dusk falls,
shadows stir and cicadas sing.

00:13:37.037 --> 00:13:39.837
The blooming moon
spills summer's gentle sting.

00:13:40.637 --> 00:13:44.038
Beneath the ink-black sky,
the moonlight gleams.

00:13:44.637 --> 00:13:48.038
I invite you to share
this firefly dream.

00:13:58.958 --> 00:14:00.077
Xiaoyu.

00:14:02.078 --> 00:14:03.158
Xiaoyu?

00:14:04.517 --> 00:14:05.638
Xiaoyu.

00:14:06.637 --> 00:14:07.678
Where are you?

00:14:37.838 --> 00:14:38.597
You mean to say

00:14:38.598 --> 00:14:40.318
they are as beautiful as the moonlight?

00:15:08.358 --> 00:15:09.278
Xiaoyu.

00:15:11.277 --> 00:15:12.318
Thank you.

00:15:14.838 --> 00:15:16.158
Since I learned

00:15:16.238 --> 00:15:18.318
that my family stole Miss Zhilou's

00:15:18.598 --> 00:15:20.038
and Miss Yue's lives,

00:15:20.517 --> 00:15:22.757
I have been afraid
to face my mother and sister.

00:15:23.118 --> 00:15:25.077
But they are still my closest kin.

00:15:25.358 --> 00:15:27.318
How should I atone for them?

00:15:36.318 --> 00:15:37.477
Xiaoyu,

00:15:38.078 --> 00:15:39.918
have I upset you again?

00:15:54.478 --> 00:15:55.558
Xiaoyu.

00:15:56.157 --> 00:15:57.117
Take a look.

00:15:57.118 --> 00:16:00.798
This is what I found among the herbs
that were delivered today.

00:16:03.838 --> 00:16:06.477
(What kind of flower is this?)

00:16:07.157 --> 00:16:07.957
You can find this

00:16:07.958 --> 00:16:09.957
everywhere in Feng Manor.

00:16:10.198 --> 00:16:10.756
It is actually

00:16:10.757 --> 00:16:11.997
a type of medicinal herb.

00:16:11.998 --> 00:16:13.877
Its roots, stems, flowers,

00:16:13.878 --> 00:16:15.636
and seeds can all be used in medicine.

00:16:15.637 --> 00:16:16.916
The most common ailments it treats

00:16:16.917 --> 00:16:18.036
are bruises and injuries.

00:16:18.037 --> 00:16:19.158
It can reduce swelling.

00:16:19.358 --> 00:16:20.756
I used to often use it

00:16:20.757 --> 00:16:22.678
to treat my own bruises.

00:16:22.878 --> 00:16:23.678
But

00:16:23.718 --> 00:16:24.676
in the village,

00:16:24.677 --> 00:16:26.237
many other ladies

00:16:26.238 --> 00:16:29.318
use its flowers and leaves
to dye their nails.

00:16:35.557 --> 00:16:37.237
I used to often think,

00:16:37.238 --> 00:16:40.398
if only I had a close friend,

00:16:40.598 --> 00:16:42.197
I could be like

00:16:42.198 --> 00:16:43.717
the other ladies in the village,

00:16:44.198 --> 00:16:46.156
dyeing each other's nails,

00:16:46.157 --> 00:16:48.877
chatting about the happiest things,

00:16:49.358 --> 00:16:52.757
and waiting for our nails
to turn red and beautiful.

00:16:54.838 --> 00:16:57.318
I think the heavens

00:16:57.397 --> 00:16:58.918
must have heard my wish.

00:16:58.998 --> 00:16:59.916
So

00:16:59.917 --> 00:17:01.957
they sent you to be by my side.

00:17:02.118 --> 00:17:06.038
(I want pretty nails too.)

00:17:08.078 --> 00:17:08.756
Wait.

00:17:08.757 --> 00:17:09.997
I'll make it now.

00:17:12.397 --> 00:17:13.477
What is that?

00:17:13.675 --> 00:17:15.557
(Encyclopedia of Seventy-Two Illnesses)

00:17:15.558 --> 00:17:17.757
Has the apothecary
assigned you new tasks again?

00:17:17.758 --> 00:17:19.517
I can help you share some of the burden.

00:17:29.598 --> 00:17:32.398
You want to cure Li Yan's eyes,
don't you?

00:17:36.118 --> 00:17:38.236
But it will be very difficult

00:17:38.237 --> 00:17:39.757
to do that.

00:17:41.118 --> 00:17:44.757
(No matter the hardship,
I'm not afraid.)

00:17:45.038 --> 00:17:46.678
Whatever you wish to do,

00:17:47.118 --> 00:17:48.438
I will surely help you,

00:17:48.558 --> 00:17:50.438
just like you helped me.

00:18:12.477 --> 00:18:13.797
Still haven't found her?

00:18:14.078 --> 00:18:15.597
It only took a blink.

00:18:15.598 --> 00:18:17.237
It's not like Yue can fly.

00:18:18.917 --> 00:18:19.997
Right.

00:18:20.437 --> 00:18:22.236
Have you asked Chu Xiaoyu?

00:18:22.237 --> 00:18:24.237
Wasn't she in the garden that day?

00:18:24.518 --> 00:18:26.078
She should have seen something.

00:18:27.637 --> 00:18:28.717
Your Grace,

00:18:29.477 --> 00:18:32.557
I would never allow anyone
to come and go from the dungeon,

00:18:33.318 --> 00:18:34.638
unless...

00:18:35.197 --> 00:18:36.477
Right.

00:18:37.038 --> 00:18:38.277
Funny how it was

00:18:38.278 --> 00:18:40.957
that wretched woman
handling the body transport.

00:18:42.118 --> 00:18:44.358
Well, well, Xiaoyu.

00:18:45.237 --> 00:18:47.037
Bring her here.

00:18:47.318 --> 00:18:48.398
Yes, Your Grace.

00:19:13.037 --> 00:19:18.811
♪Like petals fall, gone with the clouds♪

00:19:18.812 --> 00:19:24.807
♪Like stars fade fast in open skies♪

00:19:24.924 --> 00:19:30.623
♪Like snowflakes melting softly
in the evening haze♪

00:19:30.624 --> 00:19:36.948
♪Like your fleeting glance
that gave me one brief dream's grace♪

00:19:36.949 --> 00:19:42.882
♪Like fireflies flicker
through wild grass, fleeting light♪

00:19:43.049 --> 00:19:48.619
♪Like evening breeze
that stirs soft hair in twilight♪

00:19:48.899 --> 00:19:54.623
♪Like fleeting thoughts
that surge and then unwind♪

00:19:54.624 --> 00:20:00.561
♪Chance meetings fade,
just empty rooms left behind♪

00:20:00.562 --> 00:20:06.194
♪You brought a wave
that stirred a wild, restless sea♪

00:20:06.474 --> 00:20:12.369
♪Light as a feather,
yet it sank an island deep in me♪

00:20:12.549 --> 00:20:19.107
♪In that one moment,
life's grip I couldn't break or sway♪

00:20:19.112 --> 00:20:24.869
♪Leaving me lost in memories,
small and fading away♪